    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">《忆境》的世界满目沙原，漫天星辰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>旅梦、反抗、装饰</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >奇异之地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/59f2511f4c682eafc17e997e4a56d468.poster.avif?t=1772069542\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/59f2511f4c682eafc17e997e4a56d468.webm?t=1772069542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/59f2511f4c682eafc17e997e4a56d468.mp4?t=1772069542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梦界不拘规则，无谓类型。前一秒还是21世纪简简单单的学校，下一秒，蜡铸城堡便映入眼帘。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不止面具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/7e4222226cba04e4ca36d9aaca2bbcbb.poster.avif?t=1772069542\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/7e4222226cba04e4ca36d9aaca2bbcbb.webm?t=1772069542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/7e4222226cba04e4ca36d9aaca2bbcbb.mp4?t=1772069542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绝大部分装备都会改变你的能力，甚至改变你遇到的实体。一件防具可以左右负面效果的持续时间，而有一块面具则会改变敌人攻击的方式。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用后补充</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/dab10199d12f08b7c2f3aad2ccdf9495.poster.avif?t=1772069542\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/dab10199d12f08b7c2f3aad2ccdf9495.webm?t=1772069542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/dab10199d12f08b7c2f3aad2ccdf9495.mp4?t=1772069542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你获得的所有物品用后都不会消失，消耗品会在某些节点自动补满；物品重复获取可以升级，不过等级存在上限。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的空间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/fa9b78c4829f131b49e3e33a77743ede.poster.avif?t=1772069542\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/fa9b78c4829f131b49e3e33a77743ede.webm?t=1772069542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294440/extras/fa9b78c4829f131b49e3e33a77743ede.mp4?t=1772069542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个梦境世界好像还有一个神秘的地方，可以由你掌控。</p>",
